 abstract={The data correspond to measurements along a vertical line of sight carried out by the multiwavelength Raman / elastic EARLINET/ACTRIS lidar at Universitat Polit\`{e}cnica de Catalunya (UPC, Barcelona, Spain) on March, 11th 2020 and on March 21th 2020.\\
