 author={Elmar {Albers} and Alexander {Diehl} and Jessica N {Fitzsimmons} and Laramie T {Jensen} and Frieder {Klein} and Jill M {McDermott} and Autun {Purser} and Jeffrey S {Seewald} and Maren {Walter} and Gunter {Wegener} and Wolfgang {Bach} and Antje {Boetius} and Christopher R {German}},
