 author={Tatiana S {Klyuvitkina} and Ekaterina A {Novichkova} and Elizaveta A {Agafonova} and Lubov A {Lozinskaia} and Karina S {Iakimova} and Alexander G {Matul} and Maria P {Chekhovskaya} and Rahul {Mohan} and Anne {de Vernal}},
